
Quick README for Archi2 project

 * goals :
	* write a RISC-like CPU in VHDL
	* test it on a Spartan3 FPGA with a custom program
 
 * tools : 
	* ghdl for simulation
		
		# build testbench
		$ ghdl -m --ieee=synopsys -fexplicit testbench
		
		# run testbench
		$ ./testbench --stop-time=15us --vcd=testbench.vcd
		
	* gtkwave to view simulation results (waveforms)
		
		# view testbench results
		$ gtkwave testbench.vcd
		
	* Xilinx cli tools (via build.sh) to create bitstream for Spartan3 FPGA
		
		# complete build sequence
		$ ./build.sh
		
	* homemade modular assembler
		
		# ./assembler assembler/opcodes.js demo/demo.asm
		
	* simple wrapper script for ghdl and gtkwave (sim) :
		$ ./sim testbench 15us -d -s testbench.sav

 * specs : see cdc2010.pdf

 * extensions : see todo

